Ekuqaleni waqala ibhizinisi njengoba Memphis Queen Line, Med Memphis Queen II, zu ku zamadili sternwheeler, okuyinto yakhelwa uCaptain. Ed Langford i 1955 av Dubuque Isikebhe futhi Boiler Works. UMalema noma ngubani omunye othintekayo - banethuba lokunikeza inkantolo izizathu zokuthi kungani isinqumo sokudliwa kwempahla kumele singenziwa, ungakashayi u-10:00 ngoMsombuluko. Ngesonto eledlule, ummeli kaMalema, uTumi Mokwena, uveze ukuthi leli lungu elisha lePhalamende lizosiphikisa isinqumo sokudlelwa impahla. Ngo-Ephreli, kwasungulwa isikhwama esizoqongelela imali yokukhokhela uMalema isikweletu sakhe sentela sika-R16 million, kepha akucaci noma le mali isihlangene na. Michael Schumacher uMichael Schumacher noma uSchumi (wazalwa ngomhlaka 3 Januwali(ngoMasingane) 1969) ungumshayeli weFormula 1 osuka eJalimani. Okwamanje usehlanganyele neqembu le Mercedes GP, futhi umlingani ashayela naye nguNico Rosberg. Kusukela ngo1994 kuya ku1995 uSchumi wayengumpetha womhlaba neqembu le Benetton Formula. Ngomnyaka ka2000 kuze kufikele emnyakeni wa2004, uSchumi wayengumpetha womhlaba neqembu le Scuderia Ferrari. Isifo somiyane sibulale abaningi eDarfur 2012-11-07 10:01 Khartoum - Isibalo sabantu okukholakala ukuthi babulawe yisifo somiyane i-yellow fever eDarfur, eSudan, sesifinyelele ku-67, kusho abezempilo ezweni ngoLwesibili. Umbiko wehhovisi lezempilo noweWorld Health Organisation uthe: "Kusukela ngoNovemba 5, 2012, bangu-194 okubikwe ukuthi bangenwe yilesi sifo, kuhlanganisa nabangu-67 ababulewe yisona." Kusukela esontweni lokugcina kuSepthemba, kubikwe ngalesi sifo ezifundeni ezingu-17 zaseDarfur. Ngeledlule ihhovisi lezempilo lithe kubikwe ukuthi bangu-84 abanaso ezifundeni ezimbili kwafa abangu-32. INTATHELI YESOLEZWE ABAPHUZAYO nababhemayo bazokhokha okuthe xaxa kulonyaka. Ethula isabelomali salo nyaka uNgqongqoshe wezeziMali uMnuz Pravin Gordhan, uthe abaphuzayo bazokhokha 7c ngaphezulu ukuthenga ikani elilodwa likabhiya. Ugwayi uzonyuka ngo-60c iphakethe. Ibhodlela lewayini lizobiza u-15c ngaphezulu. Imali yama-cider nezinye iziphuzo ezidakayo ezithakwe ngezithelo zizonyuka ngo-7c ilitha. Ibhodlela likagologo elingu-750ml lizobiza u-R3.60 ngaphezulu kusuka ekuqaleni kuka-Ephreli. Abaphuza ijuba bona bazokhokha kancane. Abashayeli bazozwela njengoba bezokhokha u-23c ngaphezulu uma befaka uphethiloli kusuka ngo-Ephreli 3. Ilevi kaphethiloli izonyuka ifike ku-15c ilitha, u-8c uzoya esikhwameni sezingozi, i-Road Accident Fund. Abathengi ngeke bakujabulele ukuzwa ukuthi uplasitiki ezitolo uzonyuka usuka ku-4c uye ku-6c kulo nyaka.
